<SLUG> BC-FAUCET-ART-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PFIRST PLACE PFINISH
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By ROBERT MONROE 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
