   TECH-LUCENT (North Andover, Mass.) _ Lucent Technologies, the
Bell Labs spinoff from the old Ma Bell empire, has been one of the
strongest performers in the telecommunications arena for the past
decade. But after several earnings shocks, a fresh wave of
competition and some dissension in the ranks, its stock has sunk to
near its 52-week low. By Peter J. Howe. 1900 words. PHOTO
</P>
