   TECH-LUCIRA (Undated) _ SecurePC, a new product due out this
fall, can track a missing or stolen laptop computer once it is
connected to the Internet. It is the first product of Lucira
Technologies, which recently secured first round funding from a
group of investors. By Ross Kerber. 750 words.
</P>
