   TECH-VENTURE (Undated) _ Boston University's venture fund has
been around, believe it or not, for about 25 years. But the group
has suddenly jumped into the mainstream, doing deals at a rapid
pace. In fact, they're the 18th-most active in Boston, according to
PriceWaterhouse. By Beth Healy.
</P>
