<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-12 17:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0817 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r v BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX     09-12 0425
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX </SLUG>
 
 
