<HEADER>
A1041 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-ELIMINATE-ATTACK-AD-R     09-12 0034
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-ATTACK-AD-RULES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   ATTACK-AD-RULES (Undated) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Sept. 12.
</P>
</TEXT>
