stay and why you need to adhere to the rules.
</P>
<P>
   I'd like to hear from readers describing their experiences n
good or bad n with new company travel policies. Meanwhile, let's
give the travel departments their due and look at what they're
facing.
</P>
<P>
   Companies in the United States spent about $185 billion on
business travel last year, according to the Institute of Business
