<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-12 21:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1166 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-DOWD-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      09-12 0776
